# Setup: fresh page load; added two options each to wheels 0-3 via HTMX forms
# (click on Add button) so QF1 and QF2 battles could resolve.
#
# Note: The ui: block's example commands used pseudo-options (--step, --at,
# --watch) not supported by this rodney build. Equivalent probes were run with
# rodney click / sleep / assert / js.

## Probe A — pointer hidden during spin (t ≈ 2000ms after battle click)
Command:
  uvx rodney click '#battle-btn-qf1 button' && \
  uvx rodney sleep 2 && \
  uvx rodney screenshot docs/evidence/34/02-battle-qf1-t2000-hidden.png && \
  uvx rodney assert '((all)=>all.length===0 || Array.from(all).every(p=>getComputedStyle(p).display==="none" || getComputedStyle(p).opacity==="0"))(document.querySelectorAll("#battle-pointer"))' -m 'Run A: pointer hidden at t=2000ms'
Result: PASS
Screenshot: docs/evidence/34/02-battle-qf1-t2000-hidden.png

## Probe B — pointer visible and centered on winner slot (t ≈ 4000ms)
Command:
  uvx rodney sleep 2 && \
  uvx rodney screenshot docs/evidence/34/03-battle-qf1-t4000-visible.png && \
  uvx rodney assert '((all,items)=>{const p=all[0]; if(!p)return false; const cs=getComputedStyle(p); const r=p.getBoundingClientRect(); const w=items.find(i=>i.winner===true); if(!w)return false; const slot=document.getElementById(w.slotID); if(!slot)return false; const sr=slot.getBoundingClientRect(); return cs.display!=="none" && parseFloat(cs.opacity)>0.1 && r.width>0 && Math.abs((r.left+r.width/2)-(sr.left+sr.width/2))<=10 && Math.abs((r.top+r.height/2)-(sr.top+sr.height/2))<=10;})(document.querySelectorAll("#battle-pointer"), window.__lastSpinItems)' -m 'Run B: pointer visible + centered at winner slot at t=4000ms'
Result: PASS
Screenshot: docs/evidence/34/03-battle-qf1-t4000-visible.png

