## Probe E — solo-spin guard: pointer never visible over ~10.5s window
Command:
  uvx rodney js '(()=>{
    const start = performance.now();
    const violations=[];
    function check(label){
      const all=document.querySelectorAll("#battle-pointer");
      for(var i=0;i<all.length;i++){
        const cs=getComputedStyle(all[i]);
        if(cs.display!=="none" && cs.opacity!=="0") violations.push({label,display:cs.display,opacity:cs.opacity});
      }
    }
    htmx.ajax("POST","/wheel/0/spin",{source:document.querySelector("#wheel-slot-1-0"), target:"#wheel-slot-1-0", swap:"outerHTML"});
    const delays=[500,2500,4500,6500,8500,10500];
    return Promise.all(delays.map(d=>new Promise(resolve=>setTimeout(()=>{check(d); resolve();},d)))).then(()=>({violations,elapsed:performance.now()-start}));
  })()'
Result: PASS (violations: [], elapsed: ~10512ms)
Screenshot: docs/evidence/34/06-solo-spin-pointer-hidden.png

## Summary
All deterministic rodney probes PASS.
